nt-weight:normal">
<a name=3D"art14=A73ii"></a>II - pre=E7o fixo mais remunera=E7=E3o vari=E1v=
el de incentivo;</span></p>
<p class=3D"texto1" style=3D"text-indent: 1.0cm; line-height: normal; margi=
n-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px" align=3D"justify">
<span style=3D"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;fo=
nt-weight:normal">
<a name=3D"art14=A73iii"></a>III - reembolso de custos sem remunera=E7=E3o =
