ial=20
do projeto, a administra=E7=E3o p=FAblica dever=E1 prever em edital o pagam=
ento=20
antecipado de uma parcela do pre=E7o anteriormente ao in=EDcio da execu=E7=
=E3o do=20
objeto, mediante justificativa expressa.</span></p>
<p class=3D"texto1" style=3D"text-indent: 1.0cm; line-height: normal; margi=
n-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px" align=3D"justify">
<span style=3D"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;fo=
nt-weight:normal">
<a name=3D"art14=A78"></a>=A7 8=BA Na hip=F3tese prevista no =A7 7=BA deste=
 artigo, a administra=E7=E3o p=FAblica=20
certificar-se-=E1 da execu=E7=E3o da etapa inicial e, se houver inexecu=E7=
=E3o=20
injustificada, exigir=E1 a devolu=E7=E3o do valor antecipado ou efetuar=E1 =
as glosas=20
necess=E1rias nos pagamentos subsequentes, se houver.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class=3D"texto1" align=3D"center" style=3D"text-align: center; text-inde=
nt: 1cm; line-height: normal; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px">
<span style=3D"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif; font-weight:700">Se=E7=E3o IV</span></p>
